response.overview: On September 4th GCW presents The Art of War Games live on FITE straight from Grand Sports Arena in Chicago! The event features PBR Ladder Scramble Fuckfest: Ninja Mack vs Jordan Oliver vs Shane Mercer vs Yoya vs Jake Lander vs Gringo Loco vs ASF vs Dante Leon vs Nick Wayne  Also in the lineup:  War Games  MDK vs 440H  Cardona Open Challenge Super  Super Crazy vs Juventud Guerrera  Tony Deppen vs Allie Kat
